data.title: Starting Line Floor Coatings
data.meta_description: Starting Line Floor Coatings is Minnesota’s trusted source for top of the line floor coatings. For commercial, industrial or food and beverage applications, you can count on our incredible products and service. Contact us today at (952) 882-9498!
data.text:
Starting Line Floor Coatings is a family operated company headquartered in Apple Valley, Minnesota that can provide you with floor coatings to suit nearly any application. We specialize in using epoxy, urethanes, colored quartz, modified acrylic cement, and polyurethane modified concrete and have used these different high-quality products with great success in a variety of different settings. While we are based in Minnesota, we can serve not only our home state but several surrounding ones including Wisconsin, Iowa, North and South Dakota, Nebraska, and Illinois.

Contact Us Now!

The Starting Line Floor Coating Difference

Unlike other companies that work with floor coatings, we have 35 years of experience! Our team has been working in the field for decades and knows the ins and outs of the industry unlike any other. On top of having the best products on the market today, we also pride ourselves on having customer service to match. From your initial inquiry to the completion of your project, we will work with you hand in hand and resolve any issue that arises to ensure your complete satisfaction. When we leave your location, you’ll have a flooring setup that will last for decades and provide you with increased safety, longevity, and beauty!

Industrial

Factories and other industrial settings need to have durable floors that can withstand the wear, tear, heat, and chemicals that could be applied to them regularly. We can put down industrial coatings that will transform your industrial space while ensuring it's safe.
